description: Explore the Power of Generative AI Agents on Godmode. Inspired by Auto-GPT and BabyAGI. Supports GPT-3.5 & GPT-4.
title: Godmode AI - Unlock the power of AI Agents
introduction: Godmode is a web platform that provides access to the automation powers of autoGPT and babyAGI. It enables users to tap into autonomous AI agents like GPT-3.5 & GPT-4.
features: Access to autoGPT and babyAGI automation powers
targetPeople: Users interested in leveraging AI agents

faqs.question: Who is behind Godmode?
faqs.answer: Godmode is a project by @_Lonis_ and @emilahlback.

faqs.question: How can I get help or discuss the project?
faqs.answer: You can join the Discord server at https://discord.gg/vSzCcDDwz3 to get help, discuss the project, and receive updates.
